left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#878282">Von Lukas Aigner | Veröffentlich am 15.05.2024</font></p><p><font color="#878282"></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1712244177005" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1712244177005" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/70a7dd60-9c1a-4d6e-bb1e-c2ba5fedb3af/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/-%20Verbesserte%20Verbindung%20-%202024-04-19T173934.617.png" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1000" height="600" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1712229471702" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1712229471702"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Etwa jeder dritte Europäer leidet unter Fußschmerzen, die es ihm schwer machen können, sich fortzubewegen und unabhängig zu sein. <strong>Doch es gibt gute Nachrichten! </strong>Eine besondere Art von <strong>gemütlichen Clogs</strong>, die von Ärzten empfohlen wird, hilft vielen Menschen, <strong>sich besser zu fühlen und vielleicht sogar eine Fußoperation zu vermeiden.</strong></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753003432" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753003432" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753020114" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753020114" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/b5d8ab55-ead3-46f2-a17f-a185ee137892/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Thermo%20USA%20_22_.png" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1080" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753025516" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753025516"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1. Reduziert nachweislich Schmerzen und Unbehagen</strong></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753059830" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753059830"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">OrthoClogs </span>entlastet Rücken und Gelenke und gibt Ihnen das Gefühl, wie auf Wolken zu gehen, während es gleichzeitig ein Ausrutschen im Alltag verhindert.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Das <span style="font-weight: bold;">fortschrittliche Dämpfungssystem </span>in diesen Hausschuhen reduziert den Druck auf Ihre Füße und Gelenke und sorgt für sofortige Schmerzlinderung und unvergleichlichen<span style="font-weight: bold;"> Komfort bei jedem Schritt.</span></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753190022" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753190022" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190023" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753190023" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/Thermo_USA_-_2024-04-19T020810.234_120x120.png?v=1713463730" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="540" height="540" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="540" natural-height="540" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190046" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753190046"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2. Geeignet für verschiedene Aktivitäten für Frau und Mann</strong></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190025" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753190025"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Diese<span style="font-weight: bold;"> Hausschuhe bieten Vielseitigkeit über die Grenzen des Hauses hinaus und gehen</span> nahtlos vom Komfort im Haus in den Komfort im Freien über.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Egal, ob Sie morgens die Zeitung holen, sich um die Gartenarbeit kümmern oder schnelle Besorgungen machen, diese vielseitigen Hausschuhe bieten die perfekte Mischung aus Komfort und Funktionalität und passen sich mühelos an verschiedene Aktivitäten an.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753272291" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753272291" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753272369" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753272369" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/9_d713883e-499e-450e-8bc3-85e8e6c262dd_120x120.png?v=1713462206" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1080" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753272327" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753272327"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700;">3. Außergewöhnliche Dämpfung für Komfort</span></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753272326" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753272326"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Diese Hausschuhe sind mit einer fortschrittlichen <span style="font-weight: bold;">Dämpfungstechnologie ausgestattet,</span> die müden und schmerzenden Füßen außergewöhnlichen Halt und Komfort bietet.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Die plüschigen Fußbetten wiegen jeden Schritt und sorgen für eine gepolsterte Landung, die Druckstellen lindert und Ermüdungserscheinungen reduziert, so dass der Träger den ganzen Tag über <span style="font-weight: bold;">Komfort und Unterstützung ohne Kompromisse genießen kann.</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753359383" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753359383" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753359364" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753359364" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/ce2b2e57-020a-44a3-a646-d49d3d079b91/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Thermo%20USA%20-%202024-04-19T020340.612.png" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1080" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753359436" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753359436"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700;">4. Zuverlässige Qualität für langen Gebrauch</span></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753359400" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753359400"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Diese Clogs aus hochwertigen Materialien und fachmännischer Handwerkskunst sind für den täglichen Gebrauch konzipiert und bieten lang anhaltenden <span style="font-weight: bold;">Komfort und Zuverlässigkeit.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Von verstärkten Nähten bis hin zu strapazierfähigen <span style="font-weight: bold;">Laufsohlen ist jeder Aspekt dieser Clogs</span> auf Langlebigkeit ausgelegt, damit sie ihre Form, ihren Halt und ihren Komfort über lange Zeit beibehalten.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753522446" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753522446" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" styl